parameters:
(It's pitch dark... That's right, I'm sure I picked up a
light somewhere...)
"This place is... a school classroom, right?"\n<Yukine>\F[4]

Suddenly, what appeared before us was the inside of a
building called "school."\F[4]

I also go out of the shrine in October, so I know about this
building. I entered once out of curiosity. But I don't
understand why the door leads to a school.\F[4]

(As I thought, time and space are strange here. The presence
of the curse continues, so we haven't returned to the real
world.)\F[4]

"It's okay. No matter what happens, I will protect you.
Let's go."\n<Yukine>\F[4]\AA[F]\FF[20]

"How awful... The body has been completely mangled. Ugh, the
eyes and nose are crushed, and it's covered in blood."\n<Yukine>\F[15]
"There's something fallen nearby... Maybe it's a note."\n<Yukine>\F[4]

Do not touch it. Hide and wait it out... That thing is
evil...
(The rest is obscured by blood and unreadable.)

(What a terrible corpse... I really don't want to look at
it.)

(It's pitch black... That's right, I'm sure I picked up a
light...)

(It's pitch dark... That's right, I'm sure I picked up a
light somewhere...)
(The presence of that ghost... It continues further inside)

"Huh... The atmosphere is completely different from before.
It feels really... unpleasant."\n<Yukine>\F[10]

"What should I do... This place is incredibly scary. Anger,
sadness, hatred... all sorts of bad feelings are swirling
around."\n<Yukine>\F[10]\M[no]

"Ugh, the air is... heavy. It's hard to breathe... But I
have to save that girl."\n<Yukine>\F[10]

"Um, you're the ghost from before, right? What's wrong? Do
you have something you want to tell me?"\n<Yukine>\F[12]
"Eh, is this... a doll's body? Why give it to me...?"\n<Yukine>\F[8]
"Please... help... me, I beg... you..."\n<Female ghost>\F[8]\AA[N]

"She disappeared... It doesn't seem like she passed on
though..."\n<Yukine>\F[8]

"What is this, I wonder. It looks like a doll but... it has
no arms, legs, or head..."\n<Yukine>\F[8]

"It doesn't feel unpleasant but... hmm, just a torso is a
bit creepy..."\n<Yukine>\F[8]

"I don't really understand, but it seems important... I'll
take good care of it."\n<Yukine>\F[1]

\FFFF[52]Tips: Clicking the button on the light mark at the bottom
left allows you to switch the light ON/OFF
